{"title":"白族插秧节（外一首）","authors":["苗得雨"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":5,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"白族插秧节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苗得雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里插秧要过插秧节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动与严肃的节日结合，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里插秧要唱插秧歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动与动听的艺术结合。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边插秧一边唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽情劳动也是尽情乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有伴奏与指挥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秧官敲锣满田里奔波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣敲多快，秧插多快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快慢慢合节拍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁插慢了他向谁猛敲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲错了点又要挨水泼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秧田里热热闹闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秧田里风风火火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没人叫累，没人愿歇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化和谷物一同收获。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是人类发展史的再现，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是文化源泉的复活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动本不是枯燥无味，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快应和锣声挣脱异化的绳索。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石林游"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头立成的林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也像真的林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝叶茂密，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林荫沉沉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶险道滑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"间隙幽深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像进入原始森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像走进迷魂阵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不辨南北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知晴阴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走投无路地走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻不进地进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失魄就失魄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迷魂就迷魂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不为迷不会进来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情不痴不为情真。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"景不绝不为佳境，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艺不绝不会传神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神秘世界就是迷人的林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿意走进就为落魄丢魂。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}